www.ahnendorp.com

I bought their linkage way back in 1995 and it is wonderful. I used it for 
36mm Dells on a Type IV in a Beetle.

I am told that this is a copy of the Type III carb linkage.

Take a look at the VW part, maybe it will be perfect.

Much of the aftermarket stuff is pretty flexy I am told.


